OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fand a few showers at first this
OL,7,Fevening. Soon turning cloudier with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, these may
OL,9,Fbe heavy at times. Strong winds,
OL,10,Fespecially near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely cloudy day with some
OL,13,Fbrighter spells and showers, which may
OL,14,Fbe heavy at times. Strong
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds which may reach
OL,16,Fgale force before easing in the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
